{"lemma":"زَوْرٌ","slug":"زَوْرٌ","root":"ز.#.ر","root_slug":"ز-_-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-_-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"زَوْرٌ","root":"زور","pos":"N","occurrence_count":4},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":10,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":17},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n18385"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to incline"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of أَزْوَر (ʔazwar, “slanting; curved; cross-eyed”)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of زَوِرَ (zawira) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"inclination"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"crookedness, wryness, distortion"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"distorted chest, asymmetrical thorax"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to acknowledge as a visitor, to treat as a visitor"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of زَارَ (zāra) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"plural of زَائِرَة (zāʔira, “female visitor”)","tags":["form-of","plural"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"thorax, chest"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"lie, untruth","examples":[{"text":"الَّذِينَ يُظَاهِرُونَ مِنكُم مِن نِّسَائِهِم مَا هُنَّ أُمَّهَاتِهِمْ ۖ إِنْ أُمَّهَاتُهُمْ إِلَّا اللَّائِي وَلَدْنَهُمْ ۚ وَإِنَّهُمْ لَيَقُولُونَ مُنكَرًا مِّنَ الْقَوْلِ وَزُورًا ۚ وَإِنَّ اللَّهَ لَعَفُوٌّ غَفُورٌ"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"false testimony, perjury","examples":[{"text":"شَهَادَةُ زُور","english":"false testimony"},{"text":"وَٱلَّذِينَ لَا يَشْهَدُونَ ٱلزُّورَ وَإِذَا مَرُّوا بِٱللَّغْوِ مَرُّوا كِرَامًا"}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to call a lie, to impinge"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to forge, to counterfeit, to falsify"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to fake, to simulate"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to rig (an election)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"strength, force"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"See the etymology of the corresponding lemma form.\n\nBorrowed from Middle Persian 𐭦𐭥𐭫 (zwl /⁠zūr⁠/), and denominal verb.\n\nBorrowed from Middle Persian 𐭦𐭥𐭫 (zwl /⁠zōr⁠/)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n18385","headword_ar":"زَوْرٌ","root":"zwr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaAy^irN","text_ar":"زَايِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places. ―         -b2-  Also A camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having the hump inclining."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And, with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", A she-camel"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that looks from the outer angle of her eye, by reason of her vehemence and sharpness of temper:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA: [see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaworapN","text_ar":"زَوْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below: and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azowaru","text_ar":"اَزْوَرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) and a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strong and thick"},{"kind":"text","text":"she-camel. (TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"falaApN zaworapN","text_ar":"فَلَاةٌ زَوْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A desert not of moderate extent,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not easy to traverse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"direction"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a person to whom one repairs. (B.) ―         -b2-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"breast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chest:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its upper,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uppermost, part:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, Mgh:) in a horse, narrowness in this part is approved, and width in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"labaAn","text_ar":"لَبَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"; as the poet 'Abd-Allah Ibn-Suleymeh says, making a distinction between these two parts: (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its middle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"elevated part of it, to the shoulder-blades:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part where the extremities of the breast-bones meet together:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whole of the breast"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the camel: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azowaArN","text_ar":"اَزْوَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banaAtu Alz~awori","text_ar":"بَنَاتُ الزَّوْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ribs and other parts around the breast."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [Hence also, app. from the action of the camel when he lies down,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloqaY zaworahu","text_ar":"اَلْقَى زَوْرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He threw his breast"},{"kind":"text","text":"upon the ground;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he remained, stayed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abode."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lord,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"chief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a people; (K, * TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuwrN","text_ar":"زُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuwayorN","text_ar":"زُوَيْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, S, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zawiyrN","text_ar":"زَوِيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, as from the K, [in a copy of which SM appears to have found"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAlz~awiyri waAlz~uwayori","text_ar":"كَالزَّوِيرِ وَالزُّوَيْرِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kazubayorK waxidab~K","text_ar":"كَزُبَيْرٍ وَخِدَبٍّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAlz~uwayori waAlz~iwar~i Alx","text_ar":"كَالزُّوَيْرِ وَالزِّوَرِّ الخ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ziwar~N","text_ar":"زِوَرٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Determination:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strength of determination."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zuwrN","text_ar":"زُورٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"-A4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A palm-branch,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"straight and slender palm-branch, from which the leaves have been stripped off:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sgh, K, TA:) of the dial. of El-Yemen. (Sgh, TA.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Stone which appears to a person digging a well, and which, being unable to break it, he leaves apparent:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mass of rock,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in an absolute sense. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","S","A","Mgh","K","Sh","IAar","T","M","Sgh"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}